"A.P.228/7/11": "...having to take on this many at once... is going to be kinda rough."
"Heck of a training exercise this turned out to be!"
"Thanks, man! They kept coming the more I defeated, so I was starting to freak!"
"Oh yeah! I haven't introduced myself yet."
"Careful! We can't divulge information from the future. Dodge the question!"
"1. It's classified. I'm on a mission."
"...a classified mission, huh? I get it, you can't say."
"But I gotta call you something! Mind if I decide on what?"
"Can't say your name? What, you on a top secret mission? Hmm, so what should I call you?"
"\"One Punch Man\" is too long. Teacher? Nah, not quite. Oh, it's on the tip of my tongue..."
"I got it! Master! You're stronger than anyone I know, so \"Master\" it is!"
"Heh, calling you that somehow makes me feel less nervous!"
"So Master, I have some questions for you!"
"...not again! Echo! ...if I ignore her, I'll never hear the end of it. Damn it!"
"Next time we meet, teach me some tricks on how to get stronger like you, okay?"
